data.description: Whether you're looking for your forever home or an investment opportunity, look no further than this historic treasure found on Silver St. Filled with rustic character and timeless craftsmanship, this 1,620 sq ft home offers multiple opportunities! Downstairs is an additional 1,620 sq ft partially finished basement with all kinds of potential, and the home is situated on a huge corner lot with the possibility to subdivide in the future. Located right next to Centralia College and downtown, this is a prime location to turn this into an income-earning rental if an investment is the route you're looking for. A home with this many possibilities is hard to find, don't miss your chance to turn this into your dream!
